[1.384221, "o", "\u001b[32mTYPO3 core will be updated from 12.4.10 to 12.4.14\u001b[39m\r\r\nFetching version information...\r\r\n"]
[1.393058, "o", "\r\r\n\u001b[32mChanges in version 12.4.11:\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[37;41mBreaking changes found:\u001b[39;49m\r\r\n  \u001b[37;41m⚠️\u001b[39;49m [!!!][SECURITY] Enforce absolute path checks in FAL local driver\r\r\n\u001b[33mSecurity updates found (6 Medium):\u001b[39m\r\r\n  \u001b[33m⚡\u001b[39m [SECURITY] Deny directly modifying file abstraction layer entities\r\r\n  \u001b[33m⚡\u001b[39m [SECURITY] Prevent arbitrary access to privileged resources via t3://\r\r\n  \u001b[33m⚡\u001b[39m [SECURITY] Do not disclose encryptionKey via InstallTool\r\r\n  \u001b[33m⚡\u001b[39m [SECURITY] Avoid showing password hashes in backend edit forms\r\r\n  \u001b[33m⚡\u001b[39m [SECURITY] Prevent RCE via install tool settings\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[32mSecurity advisories:\u001b[39m\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-001\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-002\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-003\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-004\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-005\r\r\n  - https://typo3.org/security/advisory/typo3-core-sa-2024-006\r\r\n\r\r\n\u001b[32mRelease announcement:\u001b[39m https://typo3.org/article/typo3-1301-12411-and-11535-security-releases-published\r\r\n\r\r\n"]
[1.393411, "o", "⚠️ Breaking changes or security updates were found. Do you want to continue with the update? [y/N] "]
